<H1>Fireworkz:!ReadMe</H1>

<p>This directory contains most of Fireworkz's application resources.</p>

<h4>!ReadMe</h4>
<p>
This file explains the purpose of the files in this directory.
Most of these files are critical to the operation of Fireworkz
and so should not be deleted or modified without due consideration and care.
</p>

<h4>Neutral</h4>
<p>Directory containing non-localised resources.</p>

<h4>Neutral.Markers</h4>
<p>Directory containing non-localised image files used as series point markers in charts.</p>

<h4>Neutral.Pictures</h4>
<p>Directory containing non-localised image files used to fill bars in bar charts.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS</h4>
<p>Directory containing non-localised RISC OS-specific resources.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.!Sprite</h4>
<p>Compressed sprite file displayed as the main image on the splash screen.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.BuildVer</h4>
<p>Text file containing information about this build (application and compiler versions).</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.ImageSlot</h4>
<p>
Utility to set the Window Manager slot size appropriately for a RISC OS application executable from its size and AIF header information.
Replaces *WimpSlot in the application's !Run file.
</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.PicConvert</h4>
<p>RISC OS relocatable module used to convert some Windows image formats.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.Splash</h4>
<p>BASIC program that displays a splash screen.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.Sprites11.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Highest resolution (square pixel) language-independent toolbar and button sprites.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.Sprites22.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Medium resolution (square pixel) language-independent toolbar and button sprites.</p>

<h4>Neutral.RISC_OS.Sprites24.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Lowest resolution (rectangular pixel) language-independent toolbar and button sprites.</p>

<h4>UK</h4>
<p>Country-specific directory containing localised resources for the United Kingdom.</p>

<h4>UK.Config</h4>
<p>File containing localised initial application configuration for the United Kingdom.</p>

<h4>UK.Choices</h4>
<p>Directory containing localised initial application configuration for the United Kingdom.</p>
<p>The file Choices18 is used to configure the Fireworkz tool bar.</p>

<h4>UK.Dicts</h4>
<p>Directory containing master dictionaries for the United Kingdom.</p>

<h4>UK.Templates</h4>
<p>Directory containing localised template files for the United Kingdom.</p>

<h4>UK.RISC_OS</h4>
<p>Directory containing localised RISC OS-specific resources for the United Kingdom.</p>

<h4><em>Country</em>.RISC_OS.Help.HTML</h4>
<p>Directory containing help files in HTML format that are displayed if a browser is present.</p>

<h4><em>Country</em>.RISC_OS.Help.Text</h4>
<p>Text file displayed as trivial help if no browser is present to display the HTML help.</p>

<h4><em>Country</em>.RISC_OS.Messages.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Text files that are used to look up localised textual messages from language-independent tags and internal error numbers.</p>

<h4><em>Country</em>.RISC_OS.Sprites11.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Toolbar and button sprites - highest resolution (square pixel, pixel size 1 OS unit).</p>

<h4><em>Country</em>.RISC_OS.Sprites22.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Toolbar and button sprites - standard resolution (square pixel, pixel size 2 OS units).</p>

<h4><em>Country</em>.RISC_OS.Sprites24.Ob<em>nn</em></h4>
<p>Toolbar and button sprites - lowest resolution (rectangular pixel, pixels sizes x = 2, y = 4 OS units).</p>

</body>
